### NexHub API Tests
### Testing all services through API Gateway

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@authUrl = http://localhost:8082

###
### 1. Infrastructure Health Checks
### Config Server - API Gateway config
GET http://localhost:8888/api-gateway/default

###
### Config Server - Auth Service config
GET http://localhost:8888/auth-service/default

###
### API Gateway Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

###
### 2. Auth Service Tests
### JWKS endpoint (public key for JWT verification)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/.well-known/jwks.json

###
### Login to get JWT token
### @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
### Test protected endpoint without token (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/test

###
