###
### 3. Security & Error Testing
### CORS preflight request
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/test
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Authorization

###
### Test non-existent service endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nonexistent

###
### Test non-existent auth endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/nonexistent

###
### Test malformed token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/test
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

###
### Test expired token (manual test - use old token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/test
Authorization: Bearer EXPIRED_TOKEN_HERE